dci - The Direct Connect Index
    by Rich Lane <rlane@club.cc.cmu.edu>

== DESCRIPTION:

DCI is a HTTP/Jabber interface to the Direct Connect filesharing network. The
included Jabber bot provides access to an index of all files available on the
network, and the HTTP server allows the user to use any HTTP client to download
them.

== FEATURES:

Features:

- Use Xapian query syntax to search.

- Files downloadable by any HTTP client.

== SYNOPSYS:

  0. cp etc/config.yaml.template etc/config.yaml
	1. vi etc/config.yaml
  1. dci

== REQUIREMENTS:

* mongrel
* xapian
* xmpp4r
* qdbm
* mime-types
* libxml

== INSTALL:

* gem install dci

